00:10:32,988 --> 00:10:34,855
And Richard Simmons
ain't ridiculous?

302
00:10:34,940 --> 00:10:36,945
Well, now,
the young man does have a point.

303
00:10:37,041 --> 00:10:38,341
Yeah, maybe on his head.

304
00:10:38,426 --> 00:10:39,915
